Class FrameManager

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--edu.stanford.smi.protege.model.FrameManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
Disposable
public class FrameManager
extends Object
implements Disposable

The class handles most of the management for a collection of frames. It is a delegate of the knowledge base class. DefaultKnowledgeBase handles event notifications and journaling. This class handles most other stuff.

Author:
Ray Fergerson
